mojo.description:
Reads a KNX ETS project file (<code>.knxproj</code>) and generates a Java source file containing Calimero <code>tuwien.auto.calimero.GroupAddress</code><!-- this link could not be resolved --> constants for every group address defined in the project. 
<p><b>Example usage in a consuming project:</b></p>
<pre><code>
&lt;plugin&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;dev.huebl.knx&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;knxproj-maven-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;1.0.0-SNAPSHOT&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;executions&gt;
    &lt;execution&gt;
      &lt;goals&gt;&lt;goal&gt;generate&lt;/goal&gt;&lt;/goals&gt;
      &lt;configuration&gt;
        &lt;knxprojFile&gt;${project.basedir</code>/src/main/knx/MyProject.knxproj
        <packagename>com.example.knx</packagename>




}</pre>
<p>The generated class is automatically added to the compile source roots so it is compiled along with the rest of the project.</p>
